==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Disgraceful
<hw>Dis*grace"ful</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Bringing
disgrace; causing shame; shameful; dishonorable; unbecoming; <as>as,
profaneness is <ex>disgraceful</ex> to a man</as>.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Dis*grace"ful*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Dis*grace"ful*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The Senate have cast you forth <qex>disgracefully</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>B. Jonson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Disgracer</ent>⟦br⟧
